e are modelled in 3D, though the gameplay mostly follows the conventions of 2D shooters. Since your craft is a helicopter, a \"target and spin\" feature has been added, whereby you can both rotate your craft to attack an enemy more efficiently, or alternatively lock on a particular point in space and rotate around it while still firing. These actions are not automatically executed, and are controlled by the player; in order to succeed, mastering this feature is imperative.\n\nThe usual power-ups and boss enemy battles are included in the game, along with a selection of helicopters to choose from.","total_rating":74.43193804322563,"total_rating_count":7,"url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/zero-gunner-2","videos":[{"id":87917,"video_id":"dMCDbMZW8lU"}],"websites":[{"id":827516,"url":"https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10001932","type":{"id":23,"type":"Playstation"}},{"id":827517,"url":"https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/zero-gunner-2-for-nintendo-switch-switch/","type":{"id":24,"type":"Nintendo"}},{"id":827515,"url":"https://apps.apple.com/app/zero-gunner-2-classic/id1478247694","type":{"id":10,"type":"App Store (iPhone)"}},{"id":827514,"url":"https://apps.apple.com/app/zero-gunner-2-classic/id1478247694","type":{"id":11,"type":"App Store (iPad)"}},{"id":226290,"url":"https://store.steampowered.com/app/1342250","type":{"id":13,"type":"Steam"}},{"id":346495,"url":"https://www.twitch.tv/directory/game/Zero%20Gunner%202","type":{"id":6,"type":"Twitch"}}]}